sources.description:
Gambling for high stakes!
A Navy detective enlists his brother, a former gambler, to help him liquidate an illegal gaming house on a yacht near Miami.

Original title: Pari e dispari (1978) 
Also known as:  Odds & Evens / Trinity: Gambling for High Stakes

Director: Sergio Corbucci
Writers: Mario Amendola, Bruno Corbucci, Sabatino Ciuffini
Stars: Terence Hill, Bud Spencer, Luciano Catenacci
Genres: Action, Comedy, Crime, Sport
